<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011494-0061 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 003873 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 14, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 6; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
