and Jamal Mashburn of Dallas, Toni Kukoc of Chicago, Dino Radja of Boston, 
Isaiah Rider of Minnesota and Chris Webber of Golden State. Bobby Hurley of 
Sacramento was also chosen but will not play because of injuries suffered in a 
car crash last month. SCOTT HOWARD-COOPER 
