</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Death Wish V: The Face of Death," the latest Charles Bronson action outing, 
directed by Allan Goldstein, opens citywide today. Because Trimark did not make 
the film available for screenings, The Times review will appear on Monday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
